data.description: Come check out this stunningly renovated building! It has a Legal 2 flat with both units fully updated and ready for you to move in. We've added a bunch of new features like modern doors, flooring, lighting, and trim to make it look fantastic. Plus, we've upgraded the bathrooms and kitchens in both Unit 1 and Unit 2 with brand new appliances. You'll also get a spacious two-car detached garage and a beautifully landscaped yard that's securely enclosed by a fence for added safety. This property is perfect for anyone looking for a hassle-free investment or a place for multi-generational living. And the location is great too! It's close to Davis Park and Yards Plaza, and you'll have easy access to the highway. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
